descript.abstract: County boundaries for the Commonwealth of Massachusetts. COUNTIES_POLYM stores multi-part polygon features, with one record for each of the 14 counties in the state. MassGIS derived the boundaries by dissolving the COUNTIES_POLY layer on unique FIPS_ID/COUNTY combinations, with summary statistics for AREA_ACRES.
